{"name":"README - Savage Pathfinder - Enhanced","pages":[{"sort":100000,"name":"Macros","type":"text","_id":"8umX9S10NOYtqndU","title":{"show":false,"level":1},"image":{},"text":{"format":1,"content":"<h2>Active Effect Builder</h2><p>Select tokens and easily create AE.</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.savage-pathfinder-enhanced.macros-swpf-enhanced.elor2MWIF5yXaygj]{Active Effect Builder}</p><p></p><h2>Coin Manager for Savage Pathfinder</h2><p>Add/Remove/Check the coins in the selected tokens.</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.savage-pathfinder-enhanced.macros-swpf-enhanced.FxPtf0UXhy6ltHl6]{Coin Manager for Savage Pathfinder}</p><p></p><h2>Enchantments for Savage Pathfinder</h2><p>Using the Official SWPF module create enchantment items.</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.savage-pathfinder-enhanced.macros-swpf-enhanced.fu59nlKehM5P2pIr]{Enchantments for Savage Pathfinder}</p><p>You can modify the macro to use your compendium.</p><p></p><h2>Masterwork Forge for Savage Pathfinder</h2><p>Using the Official SWPF module create masterwork items.</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.savage-pathfinder-enhanced.macros-swpf-enhanced.2ISVEAecMz8Kduzg]{Masterwork Forge for Savage Pathfinder}</p><p></p><h2>Scroll Craft for Savage Pathfinder</h2><p>Using the Official SWPF module create scrolls.</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.savage-pathfinder-enhanced.macros-swpf-enhanced.8T2eds6S92GkCEmi]{Scroll Craft for Savage Pathfinder}</p><p></p><h2>Wealth Analysis for Savage Pathfinder</h2><p>Check how much wealth the PCs have by selecting their tokens.</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.savage-pathfinder-enhanced.macros-swpf-enhanced.BFRXIn8VDmZqlOs3]{Wealth Analysis for Savage Pathfinder}</p>","markdown":""},"video":{"controls":true,"volume":0.5},"src":null,"system":{},"ownership":{"default":-1},"flags":{}},{"sort":200000,"name":"Recommendations","type":"text","_id":"x2CWn30jOeN58NkV","title":{"show":false,"level":1},"image":{},"text":{"format":1,"content":"<h1>Modules</h1><h2>Official Module</h2><p>Link: <a href=\"https://foundryvtt.com/packages/swpf-core-rules\">https://foundryvtt.com/packages/swpf-core-rules</a></p><p>Some of the macros make heavy use of the official module. You can use your compendium or customize them.</p><p></p><h2>Better Rolls for SWADE</h2><p>Link: <a href=\"https://github.com/javierriveracastro/betteroll-swade\">https://github.com/javierriveracastro/betteroll-swade</a> </p><p>This module automate the rolls. SP - Enhanced add some SWPF actions to it.</p><p></p><h2>Macro Manager</h2><p>Link: <a href=\"https://github.com/brunocalado/macro-manager\">https://github.com/brunocalado/macro-manager</a></p><p>This module allow you to have a simple menu with all macros. There is also another great reason to use: If you run macros from this menu you'll never have to update the macros. This menu runs macros from the module compendium.</p><p>The macro @UUID[Compendium.savage-pathfinder-enhanced.macros-swpf-enhanced.H4HLv7rXMieoUliT]{Savage Pathfinder - Enhanced - Macro Manager} will only work with it.</p><p></p>","markdown":""},"video":{"controls":true,"volume":0.5},"src":null,"system":{},"ownership":{"default":-1},"flags":{}},{"sort":150000,"name":"Active Effect Templates","type":"text","_id":"rnPCs7ycnKO3YpgR","title":{"show":false,"level":1},"image":{},"text":{"format":1,"content":"<p>These items have a group of common Active Effects. You or your playes can easily drag them to their actor sheet and customize.</p><p></p><h3>Templates</h3><p>@UUID[Compendium.savage-pathfinder-enhanced.items-swpf-enhanced.1CQQxFnGWNt34rgE]{Active Effects - Attributes}</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.savage-pathfinder-enhanced.items-swpf-enhanced.GjPR11Yv9XvDGUEU]{Active Effects - Derived Stats}</p><p></p><p>Example:</p><img src=\"modules/savage-pathfinder-enhanced/docs/docs_ae_templates.webp\" />","markdown":""},"video":{"controls":true,"volume":0.5},"src":null,"system":{},"ownership":{"default":-1},"flags":{}},{"sort":125000,"name":"Better Rolls","type":"text","_id":"zKisy2PI2qGBYWC0","title":{"show":false,"level":1},"image":{},"text":{"format":1,"content":"<h2>Roll Automation</h2><p>SWPF actions will be added to Better Rolls module.</p><img src=\"modules/savage-pathfinder-enhanced/docs/docs_betterrolls.webp\" /><p>Link: <a href=\"https://github.com/javierriveracastro/betteroll-swade\">https://github.com/javierriveracastro/betteroll-swade</a></p>","markdown":""},"video":{"controls":true,"volume":0.5},"src":null,"system":{},"ownership":{"default":-1},"flags":{}}],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"JournalEntry.O1ZPETt1JHssPHUx"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"swade","systemVersion":"2.0.6","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1665752981617,"modifiedTime":1667332328791,"lastModifiedBy":"xg4TtZ3QavNbcK8c"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"xg4TtZ3QavNbcK8c":3},"_id":"eMwvsCXCKKX7vJas"}
